name: LeverageInu
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Leverage Inu, launched with MCAP- $ 806,921 and maintaining 24 hr volume $125000. Liquidity pool worth $365000. 
social passive trading with MemeFi on Arbitrum. Yield and Trade profit sharing powered by $LEVI. The LEVI treasury is used to invest in prominent ecosystem projects and the subsequent Yields are passed onto holders.
